auth {
  mode: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{accessToken}}
}

docs {
  # ElectronIx ID API

  Select the **Local** environment first (top-right).
  Run order for a full pass: Health -> Auth -> Machines -> Documents -> Pricing -> Users -> Organization -> Resolver -> Cleanup.
  Register captures the access token automatically; every other request inherits it as a bearer token.
  The Resolver folder hits a SEPARATE binary on :8081 — start `cargo run -p electronix-id-resolver` too, or skip that folder.
}
